                     <interp inst="t18260914-165-person1030" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with William Merry - I found three shoes on Charles Ballard, under his apron.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-165-person1031">
                  FRANCIS 
                  KEYS
               <interp inst="t18260914-165-person1031" type="surname" value="KEYS"></interp>
